  "short_text": "Reverse the String",
  "content": "Write a program to print the reverse of the given string.<hr><b>Input</b><br/><br/>The input will be a single line containing a string.<hr><b>Output</b><br/><br/>The output should be a single line containing the reverse of the given string.<hr><b>Explanation</b><br/><br/>For example, if the given string is &quot;Hurray! We have won the match.&quot;, your code should print the reverse of the string, which is &quot;.hctam eht now evah eW !yarruH&quot;.",
